PrecisTransfer to the COMMISSIONER of the YUKON TERRITORY, for agricultural and grazing purposes, of the administration and control of the entire interest of the Crown in three tracts of land, more particularly, 24 hectares lying between the Alaska Highway and the Takhini River, another 63 hectares near kilometre 1519 of the Alaska Highway, and 83.7 hectares situated on the east bank of the Liard River.

precis:
